			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Well the immigration process for students is getting complicated day by day. After several attempts to seek Visa, student are now finding it easy to go to countries like NewZeland, Australia,Canada,Germany and Singapore. This results in decrease of students to USA.IMO things should be kept sinple if you want to generate good revenue.</p>
